The paper discusses the infrastructure and services required for Grid computing, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). It also addresses the issue of security, which is a sub-topic of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR). The paper proposes a new infrastructure called Grid Bank, which involves software engineering and design (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the sharing and integration of resources, which is a sub-topic of Distributed Systems (cs.Distributed). Finally, the paper discusses the format for various records and databases, which falls under the category of Cybernetics (cs.CY).
